CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 5, reads: "'1. Delicious And Tasty Snacks Flowed Freely from food booths. Among the most popular was the A&P Company booth where Marcella Palmer and Frances Nunn dispensed gallons of Red Circle hot coffee."
TitMainTitle: Marcella Palmer and Frances Bell Nunn, in A&P Company booth, in Syria Mosque for 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
